=================
Emma translations
=================

To translate emma to your prefered language::

    $ msginit -l YOURLOCALE -i emma.pot -o YOURLOCALE.po

To update emma.pot::

    $ bash update_pot.sh

To update po file with new translation ids::

    $ bash update_po.sh YOURLOCALE

To compile translations of a language::

    $ bash compile_mo YOURLOCALE


Typical work flow for updating basque translations::

    $ bash update_pot.sh
    $ bash update_po.sh eu
    $ vim eu.po # or poedit, kbabel,...
    $ bash compile_mo eu

